MODE1       :      File SAMPLE1.DAT       File SAMPLE2.DAT       Directory SUB1           File  SUB11.DAT          File  SUB12.DAT      EndDirectory       Directory SUB2           File  SUB21.DAT          File  SUB22.DAT      EndDirectory 